      <h1 class="title-headings fade-in">Ideal Customer Profiling</h1>
      <h2 class="title-subheading fade-in" >Defining the client that you want, and that wants to buy from you. </h2>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-12 contact-side align-items-center text-center fade-in">
            <p class="contact-para">Imagine your <span class="color-highlight-light">  ideal client </span> that that fulfills your customer template checklist to the optimum,
              ranging from its <span class="color-highlight-light">location</span> to <span class="color-highlight-light">budget</span>, size of <span class="color-highlight-light">customer base</span> to the <span class="color-highlight-light">technology</span> they use -- the client that realises the
              most value from your brand. By specifying your ideal customer criterion, we assist you in<span class="color-highlight-light"> amplifying personification</span> and providing <span class="color-highlight-light">indispensable structure</span> to your marketing plan. </p>
        </div>
        <span class="color-highlight-light"> </span>
      </div>

      <div class="row">
        <h2 class="title-subheading fade-in">With Our Services in Ideal Customer Profiling</h2>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Identify Best Customers</h3>
                <p>Find the perfect fit for your solution by defining the characteristics and criteria for the accounts that could strike the best deals with you</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Secure Customer Loyalty</h3>
                <p>Maintain your client by having a firm business relationship with them, which is the key element to future potential sales and a more pronounced customer satisfaction.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Prioritize Before Vending</h3>
                <p>Sell to companies with the highest success potential of using your solution, resulting in greater satisfaction on both ends</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Chanelise Resources</h3>
                <p>Determine how to allocate your resources and time in the right direction to support your market strategy</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-3">

        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 features-item from-down slide-in">
          <div class=" f-card">
            <div class="row ">
              <div class="col-lg-12">
                <h3 class="features-medium-heading">Short-listing companies</h3>
                <p>Be hyper targeted about your ideal buyer persona and marketing activities and minimize the risk of missing obvious indicators of an account being suited for you. </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3">

        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row fade-in">
        <p class="contact-para">Find your ICP and bring the three ingredients: The <span class="color-highlight-light">problem</span>  you aim to solve,
           <span class="color-highlight-light">your product</span>  and the present and potential
           <span class="color-highlight-light">future needs </span> of your client into the
           <span class="color-highlight-light">perfect mix.</span> </p>

        <h2 class="title-headings">Connect with us to help you connect with your Customers</h2>
        <div class="col-lg-12">
          <form action="/contact" method="post">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="name">Name</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="name" placeholder="Name" name="name" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group" action="">
              <label for="email">Email</label>
              <input type="email" class="form-control" id="email" aria-describedby="emailHelp" placeholder="Email" name="email" required>
              <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your email with anyone else.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
              <label for="number">Contact No.</label>
              <input type="text" class="form-control" id="number" placeholder="Contact" name="contact" required>
              <small id="emailHelp" class="form-text text-muted">We'll never share your contact with anyone else.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="form-button">
              <button type="submit" class="btn btn-light contact-btn">Submit</button>
            </div>

          </form>
        </div>

